<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 09:15:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>英国思百吉 (Spectris) 表示中国市场疲软将持续至 2025 年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/uks-spectris-flags-weakness-china-market-spilling-into-2025-2024-10-31/</link><description>英国思百吉 (Spectris) 周四表示，在科学仪器制造商下调年度利润预期后，中国市场的持续疲软可能会持续到 2025 年初，导致其股价大幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 08:26:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/uks-spectris-flags-weakness-china-market-spilling-into-2025-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>官员称印尼将对南海事件做出适当反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-respond-appropriately-south-china-sea-incidents-official-says-2024-10-31/</link><description>周四，在一艘中国海警船中断雅加达国有能源公司的调查后，印尼在南海问题上的立场保持不变，并将采取适当行动以保护其领土。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 07:38:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-respond-appropriately-south-china-sea-incidents-official-says-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国疲软导致营收评级下调，Smith + Nephew 股价下跌 10%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/smith-nephew-slashes-annual-revenue-forecast-weak-china-2024-10-31/</link><description>由于中国需求弱于预期，英国医疗设备制造商施乐辉 (Smith + Nephew) 周四下调了年度基本收入增长预期，导致其股价下跌超过 12%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 07:17:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/smith-nephew-slashes-annual-revenue-forecast-weak-china-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>马士基在中国和东南亚出口的推动下第三季度需求强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/maersk-saw-strong-demand-q3-driven-by-china-southeast-asia-exports-2024-10-31/</link><description>航运公司马士基周四表示，第三季度需求强劲，尤其是在中国和东南亚出口的推动下，而全球供应链继续受到中东局势的干扰。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 07:16:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/maersk-saw-strong-demand-q3-driven-by-china-southeast-asia-exports-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>尽管中国、法国和英国的啤酒销量下降，嘉士伯仍维持盈利预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/carlsberg-q3-sales-line-with-expectations-maintains-profit-forecast-2024-10-31/</link><description>啤酒嘉士伯周四报告第三季度销售额符合预期，并表示尽管中国、法国和英国的啤酒销量下降，但该公司维持全年盈利预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 07:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/carlsberg-q3-sales-line-with-expectations-maintains-profit-forecast-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>印度中央银行帮助卢比在因美国大选焦虑而受到影响的一个月内表现优于其他货币</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/india-cenbank-helps-rupee-outperform-peers-month-marred-by-us-election-anxiety-2024-10-31/</link><description>印度卢比周四几乎没有变化，与本月大部分时间类似，印度央行对卢比的压制帮助其避免了唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选的可能性上升给亚洲同行带来的压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 06:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/india-cenbank-helps-rupee-outperform-peers-month-marred-by-us-election-anxiety-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>爱思强公布第三季度核心利润未达标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/aixtron-posts-q3-core-profit-miss-2024-10-31/</link><description>德国芯片系统制造商爱思强周四公布的第三季度核心利润低于预期，原因是市场环境疲软导致毛利率下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 06:38:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/aixtron-posts-q3-core-profit-miss-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>首尔对朝鲜实施新的固体燃料导弹材料出口限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/seoul-imposes-new-export-curbs-north-korea-targeting-materials-solid-fuel-2024-10-31/</link><description>韩国外交部表示，韩国周四宣布对生产固体燃料导弹所需的材料实施新的出口管制，以限制朝鲜的弹道导弹发展。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 05:36:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/seoul-imposes-new-export-curbs-north-korea-targeting-materials-solid-fuel-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>台风“康瑞”袭来，上海迎来暴雨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/chinas-shanghai-braces-torrential-rain-typhoon-kong-rey-advances-2024-10-31/</link><description>中国金融中心上海正面临40多年来最严重的降雨，台风“康瑞”预计将从南部登陆，并在未来两天席卷东部沿海。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 05:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/chinas-shanghai-braces-torrential-rain-typhoon-kong-rey-advances-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国飞机制造商中国商飞在香港和新加坡设立办事处，扩大海外业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-planemaker-comac-expands-overseas-push-with-hong-kong-office-maintenance-2024-10-31/</link><description>中国飞机制造商中国商飞公司周四表示，已在香港设立办事处，这是本周在中国大陆以外的第二个办事处，并签署了一项协议，支持香港的航班运营，以试图打入全球客机市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 04:23:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-planemaker-comac-expands-overseas-push-with-hong-kong-office-maintenance-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>人权组织称数十名朝鲜叛逃者被秘密警察抓获“消失”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/dozens-north-koreans-defectors-caught-by-secret-police-vanish-says-rights-group-2024-10-31/</link><description>过渡时期司法工作组发布了一份报告，通过对在韩国的 62 名朝鲜逃亡者进行访谈的研究，详细介绍了强迫失踪的模式。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 03:50:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/dozens-north-koreans-defectors-caught-by-secret-police-vanish-says-rights-group-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国智能手机制造商荣耀宣布新投资者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/smartphone-maker-honor-announces-investment-china-telecom-cicc-capital-corp-2024-10-31/</link><description>中国智能手机制造商荣耀周四宣布了新投资者，其中包括中国电信和中金资本旗下子公司，距离该公司表示计划首次公开募股（IPO）已近一年。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:21:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/smartphone-maker-honor-announces-investment-china-telecom-cicc-capital-corp-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>据Politico报道，美国通过与中国公民的交易确保牧师从中国获释</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-secured-release-pastor-china-with-trade-chinese-citizen-politico-reports-2024-10-31/</link><description>据《Politico》周三援引三名知情人士的话报道，美国上个月以一名中国公民为条件，从中国释放了美国牧师林大卫 (David Lin)。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-secured-release-pastor-china-with-trade-chinese-citizen-politico-reports-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国10月非制造业活动恢复扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-non-manufacturing-activity-breaks-back-into-expansion-2024-10-31/</link><description>周四的一项官方调查显示，中国十月份非制造业活动有所扩张，这让政策制定者松了一口气，尽管其他指标表明世界第二大经济体的复苏仍然遥远。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:47:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-non-manufacturing-activity-breaks-back-into-expansion-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国制造业活动六个月来首次扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-oct-manufacturing-activity-expands-first-time-six-months-2024-10-31/</link><description>十月份服务业也有所回升。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-oct-manufacturing-activity-expands-first-time-six-months-2024-10-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>